WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
I told her, "I'm pregnant. I'm pregnant."

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Please treat me gently.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Suddenly, a police officer came and grabbed my wife like this.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Then the officer with the dog knocked her to the ground.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
I am a Palestinian from Gaza.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:25.000
One day I heard that friends of mine, who were like brothers to me, had been killed

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
so I stressed out.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Then my supervisor called me and said: "You will be deported to Egypt. Nothing can prevent your deportation."

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Your wife will be deported to Germany,

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:43.000
and they will take the child, for what they call child protection.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:47.000
I asked, "Why should my wife suffer through childbirth only for you to take our child?"

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.000
They brought the racist police officers.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.000
I told them: "I am a Palestinian from Gaza"

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.000
"My wife is pregnant. Please don't talk to her."

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:55.000
They said, "Okay, okay."

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Then, to my surprise, I raised my hands respectfully.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
The video proves it. And the full video would show even more.


00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:07.000
Then an officer grabbed my wife.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Not the one who knocked her down, but another officer before him.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.000
He told her to move away.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.000
She replied: "No, I don't want to move away. Can I go with my husband?"

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.000
At least please treat her respectfully!

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.000
Then the officer with the dog knocked her down.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:23.000
I could not just stand there and watch my wife and daughter getting assulted

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:25.000
I went to defend my wife and daughter.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:29.000
They didn't like that and they made the dog attack us.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.000
They threw me to the ground.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:33.000
They kept pushing and hitting me in the stomach with their iron sticks.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.000
They dragged me until I fell.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:38.000
They grabbed my wife by the hair and slammed her onto her back, even though she has a disc problem.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:41.000
I was asking the police whether I could go with him or not.

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:49.000
Before I even got an answer, the officer next to me struck me

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.000
along with his dog.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:55.000
After I was hit and fell, a female officer dragged me away.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:01.000
She saw my stomach, and I told her, "I'm pregnant. Please be gentle with me."

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:06.000
She didn't respond. She was very harsh in her treatment.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:09.000
I started experiencing labor symptoms from the first blow I received.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:13.000
The contractions continued for three days.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:17.000
The fourth and fifth days were even harder.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:19.000
Then I gave birth to my daughter safely, thank God.

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:24.000
Whatever the reason, nothing justifies that kind of response

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.000
especially from the police.

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:30.000
They are supposed to protect people,

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:34.000
not make them feel fear and terror.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:36.000
We still have not received our daughter's birth certificate.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:39.000
Even tho she was born in the hospital

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:40.000
and we are still waiting.

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:45.000
I don't know where we stand, why this happened, or what comes next.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:51.000
I feel lost and afraid. This caused me psychological trauma.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:54.000
Now I think that the Netherlands and all of Europe are the same.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.000
Nothing will change my mind anymore.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.000
When they tell us: "Leave your country and come here,"

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.000
"We have human rights, children's rights, and women's rights,"

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:05.000
they are misleading people in Gaza.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:07.000
They tell them that once the crossing opens,

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:12.000
they should leave their homeland and come here and find your human and children rights.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:14.000
I want to send a message to the people of Gaza:

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:17.000
This is what they call children's rights and women's rights.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:22.000
God is showing you not to leave, not to take your wife, daughter, or mother

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:23.000
and expose them to injustice here,

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.000
while leaving your homeland behind.
